WEBVTT

00:00:00.096 --> 00:01:00.096

00:01:30.220 --> 00:01:32.980
Episode 08

00:01:33.680 --> 00:01:34.590
Fang Wanzhi!

00:01:35.870 --> 00:01:36.560
Fang Wanzhi!

00:01:38.790 --> 00:01:39.280
Your letter!

00:01:40.150 --> 00:01:40.560
Just a second!

00:01:41.480 --> 00:01:42.000
Thank you.

00:01:42.070 --> 00:01:42.790
Have some of these!

00:02:05.150 --> 00:02:06.070
(I've received many letters)

00:02:06.070 --> 00:02:07.150
(from Shenxian Peak.)

00:02:07.430 --> 00:02:08.750
(They're probably asking for favors.)

00:02:09.000 --> 00:02:09.870
(I didn't forward them.)

00:02:10.590 --> 00:02:12.190
(But this one says it's
from your nephew)

00:02:12.190 --> 00:02:13.430
(and is marked urgent,)

00:02:13.560 --> 00:02:14.470
(so I sent it to you.)

00:02:15.310 --> 00:02:15.840
(Best wishes.)

00:02:15.960 --> 00:02:16.870
(Stay safe and sound.)

00:02:17.430 --> 00:02:18.080
(Wang Jia)

00:02:23.960 --> 00:02:25.240
(Dear Auntie Wanzhi,)

00:02:25.910 --> 00:02:27.120
(I have no other choice)

00:02:27.120 --> 00:02:28.120
(but to write to you.)

00:02:28.430 --> 00:02:29.430
(I really need your help.)

00:02:31.150 --> 00:02:31.590
Dad,

00:02:32.310 --> 00:02:33.750
they're recruiting for the Air Force.

00:02:34.280 --> 00:02:35.120
Becoming a pilot

00:02:35.150 --> 00:02:36.520
is my lifelong dream.

00:02:36.840 --> 00:02:37.910
And during my physical exam,

00:02:37.960 --> 00:02:38.710
I heard the doctor

00:02:38.710 --> 00:02:40.000
tell the militia officials

00:02:40.360 --> 00:02:41.240
that my physical condition

00:02:41.280 --> 00:02:42.630
fully meets the standards.

00:02:43.310 --> 00:02:44.120
Still no.

00:02:44.870 --> 00:02:45.840
You want to fly to the sky?

00:02:47.520 --> 00:02:48.310
Fix the problems

00:02:48.400 --> 00:02:49.400
down here on the ground first.

00:02:50.470 --> 00:02:51.680
What problems down here?

00:02:52.240 --> 00:02:53.280
We have debts.

00:02:54.710 --> 00:02:56.800
You need to work and pay them off.

00:02:58.400 --> 00:02:59.560
If I weren't lame,

00:03:00.190 --> 00:03:00.870
I wouldn't ask you.

00:03:02.710 --> 00:03:03.870
If your mom weren't sick

00:03:05.120 --> 00:03:06.240
and hadn't failed her checkup,

00:03:06.960 --> 00:03:08.750
I'd even make her sell blood.

00:03:09.710 --> 00:03:10.800
Haven't you seen the creditors

00:03:10.800 --> 00:03:11.910
coming every single day?

00:03:12.150 --> 00:03:13.280
If we don't pay them soon,

00:03:14.000 --> 00:03:14.960
they'll move

00:03:15.000 --> 00:03:16.750
into our new house.

00:03:17.870 --> 00:03:18.360
Dad,

00:03:20.190 --> 00:03:21.400
this pilot selection means

00:03:21.430 --> 00:03:22.400
everything to me.

00:03:23.080 --> 00:03:24.710
This could be my career for life.

00:03:27.150 --> 00:03:28.000
Son,

00:03:30.240 --> 00:03:32.120
just figure out when

00:03:32.240 --> 00:03:34.310
you can pay off the debts first.

00:03:35.800 --> 00:03:36.630
If only you weren't born

00:03:36.630 --> 00:03:38.000
into a poor family like ours.

00:03:38.870 --> 00:03:39.870
If only your mom

00:03:40.800 --> 00:03:41.870
were normal like others.

00:03:43.800 --> 00:03:45.120
You're not meant to reach for the sky.

00:03:47.430 --> 00:03:48.240
Just drop the idea.

00:03:51.800 --> 00:03:52.960
Pack your bags right now

00:03:53.870 --> 00:03:54.630
and go find work.

00:04:00.000 --> 00:04:00.710
Dad!

00:04:09.960 --> 00:04:10.470
Mom!

00:04:12.240 --> 00:04:13.240
(Three months ago, my dad)

00:04:13.310 --> 00:04:14.280
(went to work in town)

00:04:15.000 --> 00:04:16.240
(and got hit by a rock on the leg.)

00:04:16.750 --> 00:04:18.800
(The doctor said he
might be disabled for life.)

00:04:19.510 --> 00:04:20.800
(He can't work away from home anymore,)

00:04:20.800 --> 00:04:21.560
(so he's forcing me.)

00:04:22.270 --> 00:04:22.830
(But I really)

00:04:22.830 --> 00:04:24.240
(don't want to give up this chance.)

00:04:25.240 --> 00:04:26.270
(Among all the elders,)

00:04:26.560 --> 00:04:28.270
(only you have the authority.)

00:04:29.190 --> 00:04:30.600
(Can you help talk some sense into Dad?)

00:04:31.000 --> 00:04:31.680
(If he lets me)

00:04:31.750 --> 00:04:32.600
(become a pilot,)

00:04:33.160 --> 00:04:34.750
(I promise to work hard to earn money)

00:04:35.040 --> 00:04:36.070
(and pay off the family debts.)

00:04:37.190 --> 00:04:38.000
(Aunt,)

00:04:38.720 --> 00:04:39.800
(my fate)

00:04:40.480 --> 00:04:42.240
(is in your hands now.)

00:04:46.920 --> 00:04:47.600
Prepare the veggies.

00:04:48.430 --> 00:04:49.310
We're having buns tonight.

00:04:50.120 --> 00:04:50.870
If chives and fennel

00:04:51.000 --> 00:04:51.720
are not ready,

00:04:52.190 --> 00:04:52.800
who will chop them?

00:05:09.160 --> 00:05:10.510
Aren't you afraid of all the mosquitoes?

00:05:12.190 --> 00:05:13.070
Thanks.

00:05:22.310 --> 00:05:23.430
You got letters today?

00:05:25.600 --> 00:05:27.120
Is there something wrong at home?

00:05:28.950 --> 00:05:29.720
Which home?

00:05:36.240 --> 00:05:36.950
Li Juan,

00:05:38.680 --> 00:05:39.920
could you lend me some money?

00:05:40.310 --> 00:05:41.000
How much?

00:05:42.360 --> 00:05:43.430
1,100 yuan.

00:05:44.310 --> 00:05:45.390
I know it's a lot,

00:05:45.920 --> 00:05:46.920
but as soon as I get paid,

00:05:46.950 --> 00:05:48.000
I'll pay you back.

00:05:49.000 --> 00:05:49.560
Okay.

00:06:02.310 --> 00:06:03.040
I'm done!

00:06:03.600 --> 00:06:04.560
Fang Wanzhi, do the dishes!

00:06:05.070 --> 00:06:06.630
What are you yelling about?

00:06:06.720 --> 00:06:07.310
I just asked you

00:06:07.310 --> 00:06:08.070
to help do the dishes.

00:06:08.160 --> 00:06:09.270
How hard can it be for you?

00:06:09.510 --> 00:06:10.240
Just go if you want.

00:06:10.510 --> 00:06:10.920
I'll do it!

00:06:11.070 --> 00:06:12.160
Don't you dare wash them!

00:06:12.360 --> 00:06:13.270
Let her do it herself!

00:06:13.830 --> 00:06:14.310
Hey,

00:06:14.870 --> 00:06:16.750
why are you always picking on Wanzhi?

00:06:17.070 --> 00:06:18.390
I'm helping her, okay?

00:06:18.600 --> 00:06:19.600
Is 5,000 yuan

00:06:19.630 --> 00:06:20.630
a small amount?

00:06:20.950 --> 00:06:21.830
She's just going to give it

00:06:21.830 --> 00:06:23.360
away to a nephew she's only met twice!

00:06:23.720 --> 00:06:24.480
If I don't stop her,

00:06:24.480 --> 00:06:25.750
how can I claim to be her friend?

00:06:26.000 --> 00:06:27.000
Fang Wanzhi, let me tell you!

00:06:27.120 --> 00:06:28.000
Just do the dishes.

00:06:28.160 --> 00:06:29.190
Don't go to the post office!

00:06:29.920 --> 00:06:30.720
Wanzhi said

00:06:31.360 --> 00:06:32.120
he's a good kid.

00:06:32.310 --> 00:06:33.160
So what if he is?

00:06:34.160 --> 00:06:34.630
They abandoned

00:06:34.750 --> 00:06:35.750
her when she was little!

00:06:35.920 --> 00:06:37.000
None of those poor relatives

00:06:37.040 --> 00:06:38.040
deserve her kindness!

00:06:39.070 --> 00:06:40.000
It's her family business.

00:06:40.000 --> 00:06:41.310
Just stay out of it.

00:06:41.560 --> 00:06:42.630
We're family.

00:06:42.630 --> 00:06:43.600
We're best friends.

00:06:43.870 --> 00:06:44.600
Unless she refuses to

00:06:44.600 --> 00:06:45.390
take me as her friend,

00:06:45.390 --> 00:06:46.240
then I'll stay out of it.

00:06:46.870 --> 00:06:47.270
Also,

00:06:47.480 --> 00:06:48.750
I'll say this plainly.

00:06:48.950 --> 00:06:49.920
He said he'd be a soldier?

00:06:50.160 --> 00:06:51.430
I think he's just lying.

00:06:51.630 --> 00:06:53.190
They're teaming up to
cheat her out of money!

00:06:56.800 --> 00:06:57.510
Come on, Qian.

00:06:57.510 --> 00:06:58.190
We can't think

00:06:58.240 --> 00:06:59.630
the worst of people.

00:07:00.310 --> 00:07:01.560
You're an idiot.

00:07:01.630 --> 00:07:02.160
Just go away

00:07:02.270 --> 00:07:03.240
and shut your mouth.

00:07:05.270 --> 00:07:06.270
Fang Wanzhi, let me ask you.

00:07:06.510 --> 00:07:07.830
You've been in Shenzhen for so long.

00:07:08.270 --> 00:07:09.390
Have you saved up 5,000 yuan?

00:07:10.750 --> 00:07:11.310
No.

00:07:11.830 --> 00:07:13.510
Did you earn every penny

00:07:13.750 --> 00:07:14.360
easily?

00:07:15.480 --> 00:07:16.000
No.

00:07:16.240 --> 00:07:16.950
So why are you giving

00:07:17.000 --> 00:07:18.070
away such a big sum?

00:07:18.270 --> 00:07:19.870
You even had to borrow from Li Juan!

00:07:20.680 --> 00:07:21.270
In that family,

00:07:21.390 --> 00:07:23.240
the only one I trust is Yang Hui.

00:07:23.950 --> 00:07:25.190
Although he's my nephew,

00:07:25.480 --> 00:07:27.000
he's only two years younger than me.

00:07:28.510 --> 00:07:29.560
He's an honest

00:07:29.680 --> 00:07:30.630
and upright man.

00:07:31.310 --> 00:07:32.870
He meant every word in this letter.

00:07:33.750 --> 00:07:34.510
5,000 yuan

00:07:34.510 --> 00:07:35.720
is hard for me to earn

00:07:36.040 --> 00:07:36.800
right now,

00:07:37.950 --> 00:07:39.750
but I still want to help him out.

00:07:40.070 --> 00:07:40.480
After all,

00:07:40.750 --> 00:07:41.680
his mother is my

00:07:43.680 --> 00:07:44.390
big sister.

00:07:45.920 --> 00:07:47.270
When I was abandoned,

00:07:47.270 --> 00:07:48.920
she went to the county to find me.

00:07:49.630 --> 00:07:50.430
And her illness

00:07:50.480 --> 00:07:51.920
was probably because of me.

00:07:53.830 --> 00:07:54.310
I really...

00:08:02.830 --> 00:08:03.950
His handwriting is good,

00:08:04.390 --> 00:08:05.800
almost as good as Mr. Zhou's.

00:08:07.800 --> 00:08:08.310
Wanzhi,

00:08:10.310 --> 00:08:11.040
I believe him too.

00:08:11.800 --> 00:08:12.630
I'll chip in 200 yuan.

00:08:13.360 --> 00:08:14.120
No need to pay me back.

00:08:14.510 --> 00:08:15.310
What are you doing?

00:08:15.310 --> 00:08:16.920
Why are you chipping in now?

00:08:17.160 --> 00:08:19.000
Your nephew's joining the Air Force!

00:08:19.160 --> 00:08:20.040
Back in my hometown,

00:08:20.070 --> 00:08:21.190
the whole village would chip in!

00:08:21.360 --> 00:08:21.720
Take it!

00:08:22.270 --> 00:08:23.720
You two idiots. I'm out!

00:08:23.830 --> 00:08:24.630
- Take it.
- Li Juan,

00:08:24.920 --> 00:08:25.560
I really appreciate

00:08:25.560 --> 00:08:26.510
you lending me money.

00:08:26.560 --> 00:08:27.680
But I really can't take this.

00:08:27.870 --> 00:08:28.270
Thank you.

00:08:28.360 --> 00:08:29.190
You have to take it.

00:08:29.240 --> 00:08:29.870
- Fang Wanzhi!
- No!

00:08:29.950 --> 00:08:30.750
Take it!

00:09:23.670 --> 00:09:24.120
Sir!

00:09:24.320 --> 00:09:24.960
Nice to meet you!

00:09:25.320 --> 00:09:25.720
Sir,

00:09:26.200 --> 00:09:26.630
greetings!

00:09:28.240 --> 00:09:29.080
Hello, nice to see you!

00:09:29.240 --> 00:09:30.320
Yang Hui is a good boy.

00:09:30.480 --> 00:09:31.510
You've raised him well.

00:09:32.390 --> 00:09:33.080
Well done.

00:09:40.910 --> 00:09:41.390
Mom,

00:09:43.150 --> 00:09:44.390
no matter what happens,

00:09:45.150 --> 00:09:46.000
don't panic.

00:09:47.440 --> 00:09:48.480
Don't get carried away.

00:10:00.600 --> 00:10:01.000
Dad,

00:10:05.080 --> 00:10:05.440
take care.

00:10:06.960 --> 00:10:07.790
The new house is built,

00:10:08.150 --> 00:10:08.910
and there's no debt.

00:10:09.720 --> 00:10:10.120
So there's

00:10:10.120 --> 00:10:11.000
nothing else to

00:10:11.150 --> 00:10:12.080
trouble you and Mom.

00:10:14.510 --> 00:10:15.550
You can go to the town hospital

00:10:15.870 --> 00:10:16.630
and treat your leg.

00:10:17.550 --> 00:10:18.240
It's not that bad.

00:10:18.750 --> 00:10:19.600
It may be curable.

00:10:21.000 --> 00:10:22.150
Just go with them.

00:10:22.510 --> 00:10:23.320
Everything's fine here.

00:10:23.910 --> 00:10:24.600
Don't worry.

00:10:26.030 --> 00:10:26.870
Alright, off you go.

00:10:33.550 --> 00:10:34.270
Thank you, sir!

00:10:34.720 --> 00:10:35.240
Sir.

00:10:37.320 --> 00:10:38.240
Thank you all!

00:10:40.320 --> 00:10:41.000
I'm leaving now!

00:10:46.120 --> 00:10:47.120
What a good kid!

00:10:48.200 --> 00:10:49.550
He's all yours now.

00:10:49.720 --> 00:10:50.320
Rest assured.

00:11:11.240 --> 00:11:11.870
Xiaoju?

00:11:12.600 --> 00:11:13.510
What took you so long?

00:11:14.120 --> 00:11:15.080
He's already gone.

00:11:17.910 --> 00:11:19.870
Wow, my brother-in-law is something.

00:11:20.320 --> 00:11:22.750
He forced our little sister
to build you a new house.

00:11:22.790 --> 00:11:24.270
It looks so nice.

00:11:27.510 --> 00:11:28.240
He Xiaoju,

00:11:28.630 --> 00:11:29.870
how can you say that?

00:11:30.270 --> 00:11:31.440
Your sister and I

00:11:31.440 --> 00:11:32.480
worked so hard,

00:11:33.030 --> 00:11:34.670
pinching every penny for it.

00:11:35.670 --> 00:11:36.440
But you paid off

00:11:36.480 --> 00:11:37.670
all those debts, didn't you?

00:11:37.870 --> 00:11:38.840
Otherwise, how could you have

00:11:38.840 --> 00:11:39.510
let Yang Hui go?

00:11:40.120 --> 00:11:40.670
Xiaoju,

00:11:41.320 --> 00:11:42.000
you've got it wrong.

00:11:42.320 --> 00:11:43.750
Our family's debts are far

00:11:44.320 --> 00:11:45.080
from paid off.

00:11:46.750 --> 00:11:47.790
Xiaoqin,

00:11:48.080 --> 00:11:49.670
you're a fool.

00:11:49.670 --> 00:11:50.360
You don't know this.

00:11:50.360 --> 00:11:52.000
He's been lying to you this whole time!

00:11:52.000 --> 00:11:52.600
He Xiaoju,

00:11:52.870 --> 00:11:53.720
what are you saying?

00:11:54.120 --> 00:11:55.000
What am I saying?

00:11:56.390 --> 00:11:57.630
Fang Wanzhi is

00:11:57.630 --> 00:11:59.000
our little sister.

00:11:59.200 --> 00:12:00.270
But you forced her

00:12:00.270 --> 00:12:01.320
to pay your debts.

00:12:01.320 --> 00:12:02.320
Did you tell Xiaoqin?

00:12:03.000 --> 00:12:03.790
Did he tell you?

00:12:04.390 --> 00:12:04.840
Wanzhi...

00:12:05.510 --> 00:12:06.720
Wanzhi sent us money?

00:12:08.150 --> 00:12:09.440
Don't listen to that nonsense.

00:12:10.550 --> 00:12:11.080
See?

00:12:11.550 --> 00:12:12.600
He doesn't dare to admit it!

00:12:13.270 --> 00:12:13.960
Yang Sanjin!

00:12:14.440 --> 00:12:15.030
Tell the truth!

00:12:15.270 --> 00:12:16.080
How did you pay them?

00:12:16.360 --> 00:12:17.480
Say it to

00:12:17.510 --> 00:12:18.550
Xiaoqin's face!

00:12:18.630 --> 00:12:19.080
Say it!

00:12:20.600 --> 00:12:21.080
Go on!

00:12:22.510 --> 00:12:23.200
The hell I will!

00:12:23.270 --> 00:12:23.960
What are you doing?

00:12:24.670 --> 00:12:25.870
You cheated Wanzhi out of money,

00:12:25.870 --> 00:12:26.960
and now you want to silence me?

00:12:27.240 --> 00:12:27.790
He Xiaoju,

00:12:28.630 --> 00:12:29.270
if you keep talking

00:12:29.270 --> 00:12:30.150
and make her sick again,

00:12:30.200 --> 00:12:31.320
I'll never spare you!

00:12:31.600 --> 00:12:32.790
What's going on?

00:12:33.360 --> 00:12:34.550
What? Get out of my way!

00:12:34.550 --> 00:12:35.550
Stop it

00:12:35.550 --> 00:12:37.150
Yang Sanjin, you hit my sister?
(Support Admin Watch on kissasia.cam or kisskh.org)

00:12:37.320 --> 00:12:38.670
You hit her right after Yang Hui left?

00:12:38.670 --> 00:12:39.440
You bastard!

00:12:39.480 --> 00:12:40.360
Ugh! Beat me if you dare!

00:12:40.390 --> 00:12:41.630
I'll beat you!

00:12:41.630 --> 00:12:42.960
Yang Sanjin's going crazy!

00:12:43.510 --> 00:12:44.320
Come look!

00:12:44.360 --> 00:12:45.750
He's beating people!

00:12:46.480 --> 00:12:47.200
Wanzhi

00:12:47.480 --> 00:12:48.750
paid our debts...

00:12:50.320 --> 00:12:51.030
Don't overthink it.

00:12:51.510 --> 00:12:52.240
I didn't.

00:12:53.240 --> 00:12:53.630
I didn't...

00:12:54.840 --> 00:12:56.510
Wanzhi has had it hard
since she was little.

00:12:57.080 --> 00:12:58.720
How could you cheat her out of money?

00:13:00.440 --> 00:13:01.240
Stop building the house!

00:13:01.840 --> 00:13:02.630
Stop it!

00:13:03.390 --> 00:13:04.320
Yang Hui's not going!

00:13:04.720 --> 00:13:05.750
He can't go!

00:13:16.030 --> 00:13:16.510
Come on!

00:13:18.150 --> 00:13:19.000
Let's go inside!

00:13:19.360 --> 00:13:19.790
Come on!

00:13:21.630 --> 00:13:23.200
5,000 yuan!

00:13:23.750 --> 00:13:26.080
We can't let Yang Sanjin keep it all.

00:13:28.630 --> 00:13:31.200
Whoever receives the
money gets the money.

00:13:31.630 --> 00:13:32.670
It wasn't sent to you.

00:13:33.200 --> 00:13:34.320
What does it concern you?

00:13:35.750 --> 00:13:37.720
Although it was Yang Hui
who wrote to her

00:13:37.750 --> 00:13:38.960
and asked for the money,

00:13:40.840 --> 00:13:42.030
it's still her money

00:13:42.030 --> 00:13:43.000
for the entire family.

00:13:43.240 --> 00:13:44.630
The 3,000 yuan last
time was split fairly,

00:13:44.960 --> 00:13:45.720
1,000 yuan each.

00:13:46.840 --> 00:13:48.270
You need to be fair this time as well.

00:13:48.600 --> 00:13:49.150
Let us split it

00:13:49.480 --> 00:13:49.960
equally.

00:13:51.150 --> 00:13:52.750
His aunt is just a student.

00:13:53.390 --> 00:13:54.870
Where did she get that much money?

00:13:55.150 --> 00:13:55.670
She's a student,

00:13:55.840 --> 00:13:56.910
but her family's rich!

00:13:57.150 --> 00:13:57.840
Her dad's the mayor!

00:13:58.030 --> 00:13:59.120
He has loads of money!

00:14:02.440 --> 00:14:03.550
That's true.

00:14:03.840 --> 00:14:04.320
Yeah!

00:14:04.670 --> 00:14:06.630
Yang Sanjin cleared all his debts.

00:14:07.200 --> 00:14:08.390
Someone also saw

00:14:08.550 --> 00:14:09.360
Yang Hui sending letters.

00:14:09.790 --> 00:14:10.750
It all makes sense.

00:14:14.390 --> 00:14:17.200
Yang Sanjin shouldn't have done that.

00:14:18.240 --> 00:14:19.120
I'll also ask Zhao Kai

00:14:19.440 --> 00:14:20.510
to write and ask for

00:14:21.240 --> 00:14:22.480
5,000 yuan for us.

00:14:25.320 --> 00:14:26.000
Perhaps we can

00:14:26.670 --> 00:14:27.750
get you some money as well.

00:14:31.320 --> 00:14:32.270
It's 5,000 yuan!

00:14:32.480 --> 00:14:33.120
Sir,

00:14:33.630 --> 00:14:34.910
even I feel bad for you!

00:14:35.720 --> 00:14:36.790
My mother-in-law passed away.

00:14:37.120 --> 00:14:38.120
To be honest,

00:14:38.790 --> 00:14:40.360
living alone must be hard for you.

00:14:41.000 --> 00:14:41.840
With this money,

00:14:42.270 --> 00:14:43.000
you may get someone

00:14:43.360 --> 00:14:44.720
to set you up with a young girl.

00:14:46.550 --> 00:14:47.480
You bastard!

00:14:48.790 --> 00:14:50.030
Don't talk nonsense!

00:14:50.150 --> 00:14:51.000
Please stop!

00:14:51.600 --> 00:14:53.320
Get out of here!

00:14:54.120 --> 00:14:55.480
I'm looking out for you!

00:14:56.030 --> 00:14:57.200
Get out!

00:15:03.870 --> 00:15:04.910
Don't bluff me!

00:15:05.960 --> 00:15:06.550
Sir,

00:15:07.150 --> 00:15:08.030
if you don't want it,

00:15:08.510 --> 00:15:09.270
fine.

00:15:09.670 --> 00:15:10.480
Just...

00:15:10.790 --> 00:15:11.720
Just don't be so mad.

00:15:11.720 --> 00:15:12.480
Out!

00:15:24.510 --> 00:15:25.440
You're Wang Jia, right?

00:15:25.670 --> 00:15:26.670
You're Wanzhi's

00:15:26.670 --> 00:15:28.150
best friend, yes?

00:15:29.270 --> 00:15:30.000
So you two called

00:15:30.000 --> 00:15:30.840
for Wanzhi?

00:15:32.600 --> 00:15:33.840
Last time her brother-in-law came,

00:15:33.840 --> 00:15:34.840
he was allowed to come in.

00:15:34.840 --> 00:15:36.080
Why can't we come in this time?

00:15:37.000 --> 00:15:38.440
She's Fang Wanzhi's real sister.

00:15:40.390 --> 00:15:41.440
You're from Shenxian Peak?

00:15:41.750 --> 00:15:42.240
Yes.

00:15:43.030 --> 00:15:44.120
Wanzhi told her

00:15:44.120 --> 00:15:45.200
about us, I see.

00:15:45.550 --> 00:15:46.510
Where's Wanzhi?

00:15:47.080 --> 00:15:48.550
She hasn't been here for a long time.

00:15:48.840 --> 00:15:49.910
She dropped out half a year ago.

00:15:52.000 --> 00:15:52.790
She did?

00:15:55.320 --> 00:15:56.480
Did her father

00:15:56.480 --> 00:15:58.000
get her a great job?

00:15:58.000 --> 00:15:59.000
Where does she work?

00:15:59.790 --> 00:16:01.000
I can't tell you.

00:16:01.480 --> 00:16:02.750
Don't write any more letters.

00:16:02.870 --> 00:16:03.440
She's not here.

00:16:03.720 --> 00:16:04.440
If you call me again,

00:16:04.480 --> 00:16:05.790
I won't come meet you either.

00:16:06.360 --> 00:16:07.480
Wanzhi told me not to.

00:16:09.870 --> 00:16:10.790
I brought dried sweet

00:16:10.790 --> 00:16:11.870
potatoes for her!

00:16:12.080 --> 00:16:12.480
Hey...

00:16:18.320 --> 00:16:19.360
Why did she drop out?

00:16:19.600 --> 00:16:20.630
What job is so good

00:16:20.720 --> 00:16:21.630
that she'd quit college?

00:16:26.320 --> 00:16:28.240
It must be nice having a mayor dad.

00:16:30.360 --> 00:16:31.720
My daughter

00:16:32.360 --> 00:16:33.320
is working gig jobs,

00:16:33.320 --> 00:16:34.240
and I wonder where she is.

00:16:35.790 --> 00:16:36.910
It's all because you're useless!

00:16:37.270 --> 00:16:38.550
You begged Wanzhi

00:16:38.720 --> 00:16:40.000
for the clinic in our village.

00:16:40.150 --> 00:16:41.720
Why didn't you do it for our child?

00:16:42.270 --> 00:16:42.630
I...

00:16:45.870 --> 00:16:46.360
No.

00:16:47.510 --> 00:16:48.270
Let's go see the mayor.

00:16:49.910 --> 00:16:50.870
Will he meet us?

00:16:52.030 --> 00:16:52.960
Why wouldn't he?

00:16:53.200 --> 00:16:54.510
We're his relatives.

00:16:54.750 --> 00:16:55.630
And I brought him

00:16:55.720 --> 00:16:56.720
dried sweet potatoes.

00:16:56.840 --> 00:16:57.720
How could he not see us?

00:17:15.640 --> 00:17:16.160
Juan?

00:17:16.550 --> 00:17:17.030
Juan!

00:17:17.400 --> 00:17:18.790
Get the laundry powder from

00:17:18.880 --> 00:17:20.110
my bed, will you?

00:17:20.110 --> 00:17:21.030
The new one, please!

00:17:23.070 --> 00:17:24.030
Not this one.

00:17:24.030 --> 00:17:25.720
I want the one I just bought.

00:17:26.030 --> 00:17:27.680
Just take what I give you.

00:17:27.680 --> 00:17:28.920
Why are you so picky?

00:17:29.830 --> 00:17:31.350
So high-maintenance. Fine, don't use it.

00:17:32.270 --> 00:17:33.030
Leave it.

00:17:34.070 --> 00:17:35.680
Wanzhi isn't like you.

00:17:36.110 --> 00:17:37.310
Wanzhi smells good naturally.

00:17:40.350 --> 00:17:41.000
Juan,

00:17:41.790 --> 00:17:42.830
is Mr. Zhou

00:17:42.880 --> 00:17:43.830
back yet?

00:17:45.640 --> 00:17:46.310
Yes.

00:17:47.790 --> 00:17:48.400
Why didn't

00:17:48.440 --> 00:17:49.480
you go find him?

00:17:50.480 --> 00:17:51.590
What are you saying?

00:17:52.720 --> 00:17:53.550
What?

00:17:53.830 --> 00:17:55.550
His mission is over.

00:17:55.590 --> 00:17:56.720
And he's leaving soon.

00:17:56.920 --> 00:17:57.790
If you don't

00:17:57.920 --> 00:17:59.550
settle things with him now,

00:17:59.920 --> 00:18:01.350
what if someone else

00:18:01.350 --> 00:18:02.240
snatches him up?

00:18:02.550 --> 00:18:03.480
Mr. Zhou isn't

00:18:03.480 --> 00:18:04.440
like that.

00:18:05.160 --> 00:18:06.030
Besides,

00:18:06.160 --> 00:18:07.440
we're not married yet.

00:18:07.790 --> 00:18:08.880
I can't make such a mistake.

00:18:09.680 --> 00:18:10.790
What mistake?

00:18:10.790 --> 00:18:12.680
That's old-fashioned of you.

00:18:12.880 --> 00:18:14.440
Wanzhi, you talk to her.

00:18:16.310 --> 00:18:17.310
I think

00:18:17.880 --> 00:18:19.030
no matter the era,

00:18:19.160 --> 00:18:19.960
everyone has

00:18:20.030 --> 00:18:21.960
their own principles to stick to.

00:18:22.720 --> 00:18:23.830
I actually

00:18:23.960 --> 00:18:25.160
admire Mr. Zhou.

00:18:25.790 --> 00:18:26.510
But

00:18:27.270 --> 00:18:28.640
Li Juan isn't a fool either.

00:18:28.880 --> 00:18:29.830
Fang Wanzhi,

00:18:30.160 --> 00:18:31.550
what's that supposed to mean?

00:18:31.680 --> 00:18:32.790
I overheard you ask Liu

00:18:32.830 --> 00:18:33.480
for leave.

00:18:33.640 --> 00:18:34.550
Do you dare say you're not

00:18:34.640 --> 00:18:36.000
meeting Mr. Zhou tomorrow morning?

00:18:37.440 --> 00:18:38.400
Tomorrow morning?

00:18:38.720 --> 00:18:40.030
There will be no one else in the dorm.

00:18:40.350 --> 00:18:40.790
You...

00:18:40.920 --> 00:18:42.160
Hao Qianqian! I swear I'll...

00:18:42.310 --> 00:18:43.440
- I'll hit you!
- You're in a huff!

00:18:43.440 --> 00:18:44.400
You asked for this!

00:18:44.440 --> 00:18:45.680
What are you doing?

00:18:48.200 --> 00:18:49.310
Mr. Zhou and I

00:18:50.160 --> 00:18:52.030
are going to donate blood
tomorrow morning.

00:18:53.310 --> 00:18:53.880
What?

00:18:54.680 --> 00:18:55.640
Haven't you noticed

00:18:55.830 --> 00:18:57.510
all those vans on the street lately?

00:18:57.960 --> 00:18:58.960
The blood donation buses?

00:18:59.110 --> 00:18:59.550
Yes.

00:19:01.920 --> 00:19:02.790
Mr. Zhou said

00:19:03.110 --> 00:19:03.680
Shenzhen

00:19:03.830 --> 00:19:05.110
recently passed a

00:19:05.310 --> 00:19:06.720
voluntary blood donation regulation.

00:19:07.030 --> 00:19:07.790
We may not

00:19:07.920 --> 00:19:09.160
be local residents,

00:19:09.720 --> 00:19:10.440
but

00:19:10.790 --> 00:19:12.550
we work here.

00:19:12.720 --> 00:19:14.030
And we met here.

00:19:14.590 --> 00:19:15.270
So

00:19:15.880 --> 00:19:17.240
he wants to donate blood with me

00:19:17.350 --> 00:19:19.270
here in Shenzhen for our first time

00:19:19.750 --> 00:19:20.480
as a memory.

00:19:20.830 --> 00:19:22.070
Can't you do something else

00:19:22.070 --> 00:19:23.200
instead?

00:19:23.440 --> 00:19:25.070
Blood is precious.

00:19:32.270 --> 00:19:32.920
Wanzhi?

00:19:33.790 --> 00:19:34.480
What's wrong?

00:19:38.070 --> 00:19:39.400
I recall my mom,

00:19:41.310 --> 00:19:42.110
my foster mom,

00:19:42.720 --> 00:19:43.510
Principal Fang.

00:19:45.030 --> 00:19:47.030
She told me when I was little

00:19:47.720 --> 00:19:50.720
that patients often need
blood transfusions,

00:19:50.920 --> 00:19:52.200
but there's none in the bank,

00:19:53.200 --> 00:19:54.480
and they lose their lives

00:19:55.000 --> 00:19:56.160
because of it.

00:19:57.310 --> 00:19:58.270
Later, many villagers

00:19:58.400 --> 00:20:00.200
even sold blood for a living.

00:20:02.200 --> 00:20:03.960
When I was going through her things,

00:20:04.200 --> 00:20:05.030
I found

00:20:07.590 --> 00:20:10.480
she had 19 blood donation records.

00:20:10.920 --> 00:20:12.880
Grandma Yu said there were more

00:20:13.160 --> 00:20:14.960
that weren't recorded.

00:20:17.590 --> 00:20:19.350
No wonder she passed away so young.

00:20:20.160 --> 00:20:21.750
Blood donation doesn't

00:20:22.030 --> 00:20:23.270
directly harm your health.

00:20:24.510 --> 00:20:25.030
Li Juan,

00:20:25.440 --> 00:20:26.480
you'll be a military wife.

00:20:26.920 --> 00:20:28.160
What you and Mr. Zhou are doing

00:20:28.270 --> 00:20:29.960
is an honorable thing.

00:20:30.680 --> 00:20:31.400
I support you.

00:20:34.070 --> 00:20:35.720
Listen to Wanzhi.

00:20:36.480 --> 00:20:38.440
Now I feel proud too.

00:21:01.400 --> 00:21:02.440
What's wrong? Not feeling well?

00:21:03.720 --> 00:21:04.270
No.

00:21:07.310 --> 00:21:08.400
Nervous about donating blood?

00:21:09.830 --> 00:21:10.640
No.

00:21:11.200 --> 00:21:11.720
But you seem

00:21:11.720 --> 00:21:12.720
really tired.

00:21:14.270 --> 00:21:15.790
We had mice in the dorm last night.

00:21:16.200 --> 00:21:17.510
Qian was screaming and crying.

00:21:17.510 --> 00:21:18.480
I barely slept.

00:21:19.440 --> 00:21:20.070
Ah, mice!

00:21:20.270 --> 00:21:20.880
Over there!

00:21:26.270 --> 00:21:26.880
There! Quick!

00:21:27.070 --> 00:21:28.440
Get out! Out!

00:21:28.440 --> 00:21:29.510
Close the door...

00:21:35.680 --> 00:21:36.790
I'm exhausted.

00:21:38.790 --> 00:21:40.440
I thought you'd be weak

00:21:40.480 --> 00:21:41.920
after donating blood.

00:21:42.070 --> 00:21:42.720
But seeing you

00:21:42.720 --> 00:21:43.720
carry trays just now,

00:21:43.830 --> 00:21:45.110
I think you're fine.

00:21:45.400 --> 00:21:46.070
Did Mr. Zhou

00:21:46.110 --> 00:21:47.720
buy you food on your way back?

00:21:48.480 --> 00:21:49.590
No.

00:21:50.270 --> 00:21:51.030
On the way back,

00:21:51.070 --> 00:21:52.680
I rested my head on his shoulder

00:21:52.680 --> 00:21:53.350
and felt better.

00:21:54.030 --> 00:21:55.350
I envy you.

00:21:55.680 --> 00:21:56.550
I want

00:21:56.550 --> 00:21:58.480
a guy's shoulder to lean on too.

00:22:03.030 --> 00:22:03.640
Let me.

00:22:04.270 --> 00:22:06.110
There's a little friend in here.

00:22:17.680 --> 00:22:19.310
It's a cat!

00:22:20.790 --> 00:22:21.590
Here.

00:22:22.750 --> 00:22:23.680
Where did you get it?

00:22:24.440 --> 00:22:25.720
It's from Mr. Zhou.

00:22:25.920 --> 00:22:27.720
He said it's good at catching mice.

00:22:27.920 --> 00:22:30.070
No one's looking after it
when they leave the site.

00:22:31.510 --> 00:22:33.680
So fluffy! So cute!

00:22:34.640 --> 00:22:35.640
What's its name?

00:22:36.590 --> 00:22:37.440
Mr. Zhou said

00:22:37.510 --> 00:22:38.680
they haven't named it yet.

00:22:39.000 --> 00:22:39.550
They were

00:22:39.550 --> 00:22:41.070
all guys, so they didn't
care about the name.

00:22:41.640 --> 00:22:42.270
But

00:22:42.400 --> 00:22:43.680
it's with us now.

00:22:44.000 --> 00:22:44.920
I think

00:22:44.960 --> 00:22:46.200
we should give it a name.

00:22:47.000 --> 00:22:49.200
It's a stray cat. Why should we name it?

00:22:49.510 --> 00:22:50.680
It should be tough.

00:22:50.830 --> 00:22:51.790
Mice on the site are huge.

00:22:51.920 --> 00:22:53.030
It has to be tough to catch them.

00:22:53.830 --> 00:22:54.590
Li Juan's right.

00:22:55.070 --> 00:22:56.110
The strong survive.

00:22:56.400 --> 00:22:57.270
Just like the three of us,

00:22:57.270 --> 00:22:58.240
we weren't tough at first,

00:22:58.350 --> 00:22:59.750
but look at us now.

00:23:00.680 --> 00:23:02.270
You think you're tough?

00:23:03.240 --> 00:23:04.920
I might not look tough enough,

00:23:05.070 --> 00:23:06.440
but I've been tough
inside for a while.

00:23:08.030 --> 00:23:09.550
From the day I decided
to come to Shenzhen,

00:23:09.720 --> 00:23:10.790
I told myself:

00:23:11.070 --> 00:23:11.830
Fang Wanzhi,

00:23:12.070 --> 00:23:13.510
you have to make something of yourself.

00:23:15.790 --> 00:23:16.310
Right?

00:23:17.030 --> 00:23:17.550
Right?

00:23:19.720 --> 00:23:20.400
It understands me.

00:23:21.270 --> 00:23:22.510
Look how cute it is.

00:23:22.510 --> 00:23:24.160
Let's name it.

00:23:24.720 --> 00:23:25.790
How about...

00:23:26.200 --> 00:23:28.000
Little White?

00:23:28.270 --> 00:23:29.110
Oh, my god,

00:23:29.110 --> 00:23:30.310
that's so tacky.

00:23:30.880 --> 00:23:32.030
Wanzhi, you're educated.

00:23:32.160 --> 00:23:32.830
You name it.

00:23:35.310 --> 00:23:35.880
Just now,

00:23:36.070 --> 00:23:37.680
what did you say at the door?

00:23:38.510 --> 00:23:39.640
What did I say at the door?

00:23:40.200 --> 00:23:41.030
You said...

00:23:41.110 --> 00:23:42.590
There's a little friend inside.

00:23:43.440 --> 00:23:44.640
That's a perfect name.

00:23:45.350 --> 00:23:46.310
Little Friend...

00:23:47.200 --> 00:23:47.960
When you leave home,

00:23:48.110 --> 00:23:49.440
all you need are friends.

00:23:51.790 --> 00:23:52.510
Okay, fine.

00:23:52.680 --> 00:23:53.510
Let's call it that.

00:23:53.640 --> 00:23:54.550
I agree too.

00:23:55.000 --> 00:23:55.480
From now on,

00:23:55.640 --> 00:23:56.750
your name is Little Friend.

00:23:58.070 --> 00:23:59.270
Little Friend. Little Friend.

00:24:37.790 --> 00:24:38.240
Here.

00:24:42.550 --> 00:24:43.310
Sorry,

00:24:43.680 --> 00:24:44.880
we're late.

00:24:45.830 --> 00:24:46.440
You're not.

00:24:46.960 --> 00:24:48.070
We still have ten minutes

00:24:48.070 --> 00:24:49.160
until we leave.

00:24:49.550 --> 00:24:51.400
She insisted on buying you fruits.

00:24:51.440 --> 00:24:52.750
We couldn't find a stall anywhere.

00:24:52.750 --> 00:24:53.750
I'm so exhausted.

00:24:54.070 --> 00:24:54.590
Guys!

00:24:55.440 --> 00:24:55.960
Come on!

00:24:56.590 --> 00:24:57.240
Hurry up!

00:24:57.750 --> 00:24:58.400
It's so heavy.

00:24:58.440 --> 00:24:59.590
Pass them out!

00:24:59.720 --> 00:25:00.310
Alright!

00:25:03.680 --> 00:25:05.070
You go talk to Captain Zhou.

00:25:13.440 --> 00:25:14.270
This is for you.

00:25:44.750 --> 00:25:45.830
Say something to the soldiers.

00:25:47.590 --> 00:25:48.400
Like what?

00:25:48.790 --> 00:25:49.960
Whatever you want.

00:25:51.440 --> 00:25:52.030
Wanzhi,

00:25:52.750 --> 00:25:54.030
I've never spoken in front of so

00:25:54.110 --> 00:25:54.590
many people.

00:25:54.590 --> 00:25:55.200
What do I do?

00:25:56.240 --> 00:25:57.680
They're all Captain Zhou's men.

00:25:57.960 --> 00:25:58.720
No need to be nervous.

00:26:00.110 --> 00:26:01.400
I don't want to embarrass him.

00:26:01.920 --> 00:26:03.240
Then don't think of it as a speech.

00:26:03.440 --> 00:26:04.240
Speak from your heart.

00:26:04.400 --> 00:26:05.480
Say whatever comes to your mind.

00:26:07.310 --> 00:26:07.720
Okay.

00:26:08.440 --> 00:26:09.240
I'll try.

00:26:14.310 --> 00:26:14.960
Um...

00:26:22.270 --> 00:26:23.510
I still can't.

00:26:26.310 --> 00:26:26.750
Never mind.

00:26:27.680 --> 00:26:29.270
Then wave to them.

00:26:37.310 --> 00:26:38.350
Ma'am!

00:26:38.830 --> 00:26:40.110
Take care!

00:26:40.400 --> 00:26:41.720
Ma'am!

00:26:42.110 --> 00:26:45.590
May you be healthy and happy!

00:26:46.070 --> 00:26:47.550
Ma'am!

00:26:47.750 --> 00:26:51.240
May you have a happy marriage
and start a family soon!

00:26:57.550 --> 00:26:58.030
Juan!

00:27:18.720 --> 00:27:19.590
Guys!

00:27:21.590 --> 00:27:22.550
Come to my house later

00:27:22.590 --> 00:27:24.030
and drink with Captain Zhou!

00:27:24.510 --> 00:27:26.590
I'll make you pancakes and stew!

00:27:27.160 --> 00:27:32.000
Thank you, ma'am! Thank you!

00:27:38.550 --> 00:27:45.680
♪I'll walk you to the road♪

00:27:46.310 --> 00:27:53.440
♪Your kindness I'll never forget♪

00:27:54.070 --> 00:28:01.350
♪Farmers and folks know it well♪

00:28:01.790 --> 00:28:09.480
♪Across mountains and
rivers, I'll miss you still♪

00:28:10.000 --> 00:28:17.270
♪I'll walk you under the big tree♪

00:28:21.750 --> 00:28:23.480
(Captain Zhou and his men)

00:28:23.480 --> 00:28:24.920
(left as the song faded out.)

00:28:25.920 --> 00:28:28.440
(This brand-new, bustling city)

00:28:29.000 --> 00:28:30.750
(would remember the sweat these)

00:28:30.830 --> 00:28:31.880
(builders poured out.)

00:28:32.920 --> 00:28:34.920
(The trucks were gone from sight,)

00:28:36.110 --> 00:28:38.830
(but Li Juan's voice still
floated in the air.)

00:28:40.070 --> 00:28:41.400
(We were so young)

00:28:41.400 --> 00:28:42.350
(back then.)

00:28:43.070 --> 00:28:44.030
(We always thought fate)

00:28:44.030 --> 00:28:45.790
(would be like Shenzhen's weather:)

00:28:46.310 --> 00:28:48.110
(windy one minute and rainy the next,)

00:28:48.880 --> 00:28:50.270
(but once the clouds cleared,)

00:28:50.270 --> 00:28:51.720
(it would be bright and sunny again.)

00:29:12.240 --> 00:29:13.510
I specially made a detour

00:29:13.920 --> 00:29:14.830
just to show you around.

00:29:17.000 --> 00:29:17.750
Thank you, Zhu.

00:29:21.550 --> 00:29:22.750
My dad was being unfair

00:29:23.510 --> 00:29:24.440
with the work assignments.

00:29:24.830 --> 00:29:26.270
I even felt embarrassed.

00:29:27.270 --> 00:29:28.310
Luckily, Li Juan

00:29:28.310 --> 00:29:29.440
and Hao Qianqian were busy today,

00:29:29.920 --> 00:29:31.030
so I could take you out.

00:29:33.240 --> 00:29:34.480
You've been swamped lately, huh?

00:29:35.440 --> 00:29:36.000
I'm okay.

00:29:40.110 --> 00:29:40.830
I heard

00:29:41.270 --> 00:29:43.240
you sent 5,000 yuan home.

00:29:44.750 --> 00:29:46.030
You also heard about it?

00:29:46.720 --> 00:29:47.400
We're the only young

00:29:47.400 --> 00:29:48.240
people in the cafeteria.

00:29:48.270 --> 00:29:49.240
I know everything.

00:29:52.070 --> 00:29:52.750
Look...

00:29:53.750 --> 00:29:54.830
if you need money, I have some.

00:29:55.920 --> 00:29:56.790
You don't have to date me.

00:29:56.960 --> 00:29:57.720
It's fine if you just

00:29:57.750 --> 00:29:58.350
borrow some.

00:29:58.590 --> 00:29:59.480
We're coworkers.

00:29:59.790 --> 00:30:01.030
In a big city like Shenzhen,

00:30:01.160 --> 00:30:02.480
it's fate that we met.

00:30:03.310 --> 00:30:04.000
I mean it.

00:30:04.510 --> 00:30:06.070
If you're short on cash,

00:30:06.310 --> 00:30:07.110
just ask me.

00:30:09.440 --> 00:30:10.400
Thank you, Zhu.

00:30:25.880 --> 00:30:26.480
Liu!

00:30:27.200 --> 00:30:27.750
Dad!

00:30:31.590 --> 00:30:32.240
Mr. Hu.

00:30:37.480 --> 00:30:39.160
Five, six, seven...

00:30:40.400 --> 00:30:41.640
Thirty-one...

00:30:41.920 --> 00:30:42.510
One...

00:30:42.880 --> 00:30:43.510
Two...

00:30:46.030 --> 00:30:46.920
What are you counting?

00:30:47.960 --> 00:30:49.400
According to his last letter,

00:30:49.550 --> 00:30:50.550
Shuchun has been transferred

00:30:50.680 --> 00:30:51.640
back to his hometown.

00:30:51.880 --> 00:30:52.640
I should be able

00:30:52.640 --> 00:30:53.590
to get his letter tomorrow.

00:30:53.790 --> 00:30:55.480
Look how happy you are.

00:30:56.030 --> 00:30:56.680
By the way,

00:30:57.070 --> 00:30:58.550
when he's settled,

00:30:58.680 --> 00:30:59.750
will he come pick you up?

00:31:01.920 --> 00:31:02.480
No.

00:31:03.440 --> 00:31:04.110
But

00:31:04.720 --> 00:31:05.550
in his last letter,

00:31:05.550 --> 00:31:06.480
he talked about

00:31:06.920 --> 00:31:07.960
having the wedding

00:31:07.960 --> 00:31:09.110
during Spring Festival.

00:31:10.400 --> 00:31:11.400
Really?

00:31:13.030 --> 00:31:14.350
Congratulations then!

00:31:14.680 --> 00:31:16.550
You two have to come with me.

00:31:17.160 --> 00:31:18.310
I already told him

00:31:18.590 --> 00:31:19.590
you'd both be my bridesmaids.

00:31:19.880 --> 00:31:20.830
Of course!

00:31:21.590 --> 00:31:22.400
Don't forget my gift!

00:31:23.680 --> 00:31:24.160
Here!

00:31:24.830 --> 00:31:26.240
Don't just think about that.

00:31:26.440 --> 00:31:27.440
Get her a proper wedding gift.

00:31:27.720 --> 00:31:29.030
I definitely will!

00:31:29.200 --> 00:31:30.590
My best friend is getting married.

00:31:30.960 --> 00:31:31.790
I'll get her a good one!

00:31:31.880 --> 00:31:32.640
I'm not cheap.

00:31:35.000 --> 00:31:35.510
By the way,

00:31:35.790 --> 00:31:37.160
after you get married,

00:31:37.480 --> 00:31:39.070
you won't come work here
anymore, will you?

00:31:41.350 --> 00:31:42.790
We haven't decided that yet.

00:31:43.030 --> 00:31:43.830
But we made a deal.

00:31:44.000 --> 00:31:44.920
It can't be changed.

00:31:45.160 --> 00:31:46.110
If you find a good job

00:31:46.110 --> 00:31:47.160
in his hometown,

00:31:47.310 --> 00:31:48.440
you have to take me with you.

00:31:49.510 --> 00:31:51.030
They pay less inland.

00:31:51.240 --> 00:31:52.510
That doesn't matter.

00:31:53.270 --> 00:31:54.960
If I could marry someone

00:31:55.110 --> 00:31:56.960
as good as Mr. Zhou,

00:31:57.160 --> 00:31:58.400
I'd work for nothing.

00:31:58.440 --> 00:31:59.400
Hao Qianqian,

00:31:59.640 --> 00:32:00.920
can you be serious for once?

00:32:01.000 --> 00:32:02.240
I am being serious!

00:32:02.590 --> 00:32:03.240
Hao Qianqian!

00:32:03.240 --> 00:32:03.790
- Stop it!
- Li Juan!

00:32:04.110 --> 00:32:04.790
Li Juan!

00:32:05.350 --> 00:32:05.920
Li Juan!

00:32:08.960 --> 00:32:09.640
Um...

00:32:10.960 --> 00:32:11.720
Mr. Hu is here for you.

00:32:19.310 --> 00:32:19.920
Mr. Hu, you

00:32:20.400 --> 00:32:21.070
wanted to see me?

00:32:27.960 --> 00:32:28.790
Li Juan,

00:32:30.830 --> 00:32:31.550
you are

00:32:32.200 --> 00:32:33.750
Zhou Shuchun's fiancée, right?

00:32:34.920 --> 00:32:35.350
Yes.

00:32:36.510 --> 00:32:37.480
I've long heard

00:32:38.750 --> 00:32:39.880
you're a capable person.

00:32:47.200 --> 00:32:47.640
I...

00:32:50.550 --> 00:32:51.310
Sir.

00:32:56.590 --> 00:32:59.240
I was once a soldier too.

00:32:59.640 --> 00:33:00.750
Over ten years ago,

00:33:01.400 --> 00:33:03.030
our engineering corps

00:33:03.440 --> 00:33:05.000
was decommissioned here in Shenzhen.

00:33:05.960 --> 00:33:07.000
I've been in construction

00:33:07.200 --> 00:33:08.310
ever since.

00:33:09.110 --> 00:33:09.920
Two years ago,

00:33:10.350 --> 00:33:11.160
I met

00:33:11.400 --> 00:33:12.790
Captain Zhou when he was here

00:33:12.880 --> 00:33:13.720
on a mission.

00:33:14.680 --> 00:33:15.240
We...

00:33:16.790 --> 00:33:18.920
We bonded instantly.

00:33:20.310 --> 00:33:20.830
I...

00:33:22.920 --> 00:33:24.030
I really don't know

00:33:26.400 --> 00:33:27.920
how to say this.

00:33:30.640 --> 00:33:31.200
Xu.

00:33:39.110 --> 00:33:39.920
Li Juan,

00:33:41.160 --> 00:33:42.270
you must

00:33:42.270 --> 00:33:43.550
stay calm.

00:33:47.720 --> 00:33:48.480
What happened

00:33:48.790 --> 00:33:49.550
to Captain Zhou?

00:33:50.070 --> 00:33:51.160
Zhou Shuchun

00:33:51.960 --> 00:33:53.400
was caught in a mountain landslide

00:33:53.720 --> 00:33:55.110
on the day he transferred.

00:33:56.110 --> 00:33:57.240
To save others,

00:33:58.790 --> 00:33:59.790
he... lost his life.

00:34:06.070 --> 00:34:06.920
Juan! Juan!

00:34:07.000 --> 00:34:08.110
Li Juan! Li Juan!

00:34:16.670 --> 00:34:17.400
Liu,

00:34:18.400 --> 00:34:19.760
I can't let Li Juan

00:34:19.840 --> 00:34:20.760
go by herself.

00:34:21.030 --> 00:34:21.920
She's so young,

00:34:22.400 --> 00:34:23.840
and she's been hit this hard.

00:34:24.320 --> 00:34:25.880
If something happens to her on the way,

00:34:26.360 --> 00:34:27.840
how could we face Captain Zhou?

00:34:31.480 --> 00:34:32.070
Maybe

00:34:32.550 --> 00:34:34.440
Fang can go with her.

00:34:35.190 --> 00:34:36.630
The college girl who can write?

00:34:38.960 --> 00:34:39.400
Good.

00:34:40.760 --> 00:34:42.190
I remember her name is Fang Wanzhi.

00:34:43.880 --> 00:34:44.800
Good choice.

00:34:55.000 --> 00:34:55.590
Liu!

00:34:58.440 --> 00:34:59.030
Got the tickets?

00:35:00.360 --> 00:35:01.710
Take good care of Juan.

00:35:02.400 --> 00:35:03.670
I was going to tell you.

00:35:04.110 --> 00:35:05.190
If I'm going with Li Juan,

00:35:05.630 --> 00:35:06.480
what about the cafeteria?

00:35:07.230 --> 00:35:07.840
Don't worry.

00:35:08.320 --> 00:35:10.800
The company's sending temp help.

00:35:11.590 --> 00:35:12.880
Give this to Juan.

00:35:13.510 --> 00:35:14.070
What's this?

00:35:15.920 --> 00:35:18.320
A wedding gift from me and Zhu.

00:35:18.760 --> 00:35:19.670
It's 1,000 yuan.

00:35:20.960 --> 00:35:23.070
I can't bear to go see her.

00:35:24.510 --> 00:35:25.000
I'm afraid...

00:35:25.230 --> 00:35:26.280
I can't take it.

00:35:28.000 --> 00:35:29.230
But I can't...

00:35:29.230 --> 00:35:30.360
decide for Li Juan.

00:35:30.800 --> 00:35:31.440
You can.

00:35:32.000 --> 00:35:33.760
You're best friends.

00:35:35.000 --> 00:35:36.110
Captain Zhou used

00:35:36.960 --> 00:35:38.320
to drink and chat

00:35:39.670 --> 00:35:40.630
with me.

00:35:43.440 --> 00:35:45.480
He was a good man.

00:35:46.840 --> 00:35:48.590
Juan has such bad luck.

00:35:50.670 --> 00:35:51.880
This is what I want for her.

00:35:52.360 --> 00:35:52.960
Take it.

00:35:58.320 --> 00:35:59.760
I... I thank you on Li Juan's behalf.

00:37:02.110 --> 00:37:02.630
My condolences.

00:38:29.960 --> 00:38:30.630
Hug!

00:38:31.150 --> 00:38:38.440
Hug...

00:39:19.030 --> 00:39:19.840
Fang,

00:39:21.230 --> 00:39:22.630
according to local customs,

00:39:23.400 --> 00:39:24.710
after the memorial service,

00:39:25.510 --> 00:39:27.230
Shuchun's body

00:39:27.960 --> 00:39:29.070
will be cremated.

00:39:29.920 --> 00:39:31.590
If Li Juan

00:39:32.030 --> 00:39:33.150
has any requests,

00:39:33.710 --> 00:39:34.710
she can let us know.

00:39:35.280 --> 00:39:36.510
We'll do everything we can.

00:39:42.230 --> 00:39:43.590
I have no requests at all.

00:39:51.800 --> 00:39:53.440
Captain Zhou! Captain Zhou!

00:39:53.480 --> 00:39:54.070
Kids,

00:39:54.360 --> 00:39:56.320
let's send Captain Zhou

00:39:56.320 --> 00:39:57.440
off on his final journey.

00:39:58.110 --> 00:39:59.320
Captain Zhou!

00:39:59.590 --> 00:40:00.280
Captain Zhou!

00:40:00.800 --> 00:40:01.760
Captain Zhou!

00:40:06.190 --> 00:40:07.360
They were

00:40:07.840 --> 00:40:09.000
all saved by Shuchun

00:40:09.150 --> 00:40:11.630
from the landslide.

00:40:12.800 --> 00:40:14.070
We're so sorry!

00:40:14.110 --> 00:40:15.230
Captain Zhou!

00:40:16.880 --> 00:40:18.840
An old lady's life like mine
isn't worth much,

00:40:19.630 --> 00:40:20.440
but a great captain

00:40:20.440 --> 00:40:21.960
like you passed away because of me...

00:40:23.400 --> 00:40:24.150
Please don't say that.

00:40:26.760 --> 00:40:28.480
Seeing you safe and sound

00:40:30.670 --> 00:40:32.550
is all Captain Zhou would want.

00:41:04.880 --> 00:41:05.590
Get up.

00:41:06.630 --> 00:41:07.400
Child,

00:41:08.360 --> 00:41:09.190
get up.

00:41:09.920 --> 00:41:11.030
Let me feel you.

00:41:11.230 --> 00:41:11.800
Come on.

00:41:23.880 --> 00:41:25.360
Look at you,

00:41:26.800 --> 00:41:28.710
so pretty and elegant.

00:41:29.480 --> 00:41:31.480
Shuchun was right about you.

00:41:35.030 --> 00:41:37.070
But he didn't get to
enjoy life with you.

00:41:47.590 --> 00:41:48.230
Mom,

00:41:50.960 --> 00:41:52.320
please come to Shenzhen with me.

00:41:54.280 --> 00:41:55.760
I'll take care of you from now on.

00:41:56.190 --> 00:41:56.800
You...

00:41:57.630 --> 00:41:59.360
What did you just call me?

00:42:00.000 --> 00:42:01.440
Say it again.

00:42:03.150 --> 00:42:03.670
Mom!

00:42:13.630 --> 00:42:14.280
This...

00:42:14.800 --> 00:42:16.030
is the money Shuchun sent me

00:42:16.230 --> 00:42:17.480
all these years.

00:42:17.760 --> 00:42:19.070
I saved it all.

00:42:19.670 --> 00:42:21.550
I plan to give it to my daughter-in-law

00:42:22.150 --> 00:42:23.480
when she calls me Mom.

00:42:24.510 --> 00:42:25.110
Take it.

00:42:25.150 --> 00:42:25.710
Mom,

00:42:26.920 --> 00:42:28.150
I can't take it.

00:42:28.800 --> 00:42:29.670
If you don't take it,

00:42:30.710 --> 00:42:32.190
you don't accept me as your mom.

00:42:32.280 --> 00:42:33.030
No...

00:42:33.630 --> 00:42:34.670
You just called me Mom.

00:42:35.030 --> 00:42:36.590
You must take it. Go on.

00:42:43.840 --> 00:42:44.400
Mom...

00:42:45.510 --> 00:42:46.110
Mom...

00:42:48.030 --> 00:42:48.840
Mom!

00:42:50.150 --> 00:42:50.840
Mom...